subject: Poker (Card Game)
World Series of Poker
lead_paragraph: The Canadian poker professional Jonathan Duhamel won the World Series of Poker main event title and $8.94 million Monday night in Las Vegas after keeping a stranglehold on his chips and pressuring his opponent.
